          "@type": "Answer",
          "text":"You can return your item within 60 days provided the product is in its original, unused condition."}
        },{
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How Do I Return an Item?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text":"Please follow the instructions displayed on our returns page."}
        },{
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can I Send My Item Back for An Exchange?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text":"Unfortunately, we are no longer able to offer exchanges. If you require an alternative item, we recommend placing a new order and returning your unwanted shoes to us."}
        },{
        "@type": "Question",
